===Noun===
'''arccosine''' (''plural'' '''arccosines''')

#{{trigonometry}} Any of several [[single-valued]] or [[multivalued]] functions that are inverses of the [[cosine]] function. Symbol: [[arccos]], cos<sup>-1</sup>

